{
  "page": "Humfrey Clifton",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Clifton\" title=\"House Clifton\"><img alt=\"None.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/50px-None.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/75px-None.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/100px-None.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Ser</span><br />Humfrey Clifton</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Clifton\" title=\"House Clifton\"><img alt=\"None.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/50px-None.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/75px-None.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/58/None.svg/100px-None.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Clifton\" title=\"House Clifton\">House Clifton</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Baratheon_of_Dragonstone\" title=\"House Baratheon of Dragonstone\">House Baratheon of Dragonstone</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Westermen\" title=\"Westermen\">Westermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (appears)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Humfrey Clifton</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Clifton\" title=\"House Clifton\">House Clifton</a>. He is a <a href=\"/index.php/Sworn_sword\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sworn sword\">sworn sword</a> in service to King <a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis I Baratheon</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> His relation to the head of the house, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Gareth_Clifton\" title=\"Gareth Clifton\">Gareth Clifton</a>, is unknown.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Humfrey_Clifton&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Humfrey_Clifton&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Ser Humfrey accompanies <a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis Baratheon</a> in his <a href=\"/index.php/March_on_Winterfell\" title=\"March on Winterfell\">march on Winterfell</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">north</a>. When they become stranded at the <a href=\"/index.php/Crofter%27s_village\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Crofter&#39;s village\">crofter's village</a>, Humfrey insists they press on, as they will die from cold and starvation if they stay. When <a href=\"/index.php/Ned_Woods\" title=\"Ned Woods\">Ned Woods</a> concludes that the lake has been emptied by the fishermen, Humfrey insists that the lack of food is all the more reason to march, stating \"<i>If death is our fate, let us die with swords in hand.</i>\"<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Humfrey_Clifton&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd62.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_62\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 62\">Chapter 62</a>, The Sacrifice.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403122111\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.123 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.915 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 573/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10460/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 5711/2097152 by